snippet.title: Car For Sale Simulator 2023 - Release v1.0
snippet.description:
Hello Dear Players,

We are excited and proud to announce the official release of the full version of Car For Sale Simulator 2023! 🎉

Your support and feedback during Early Access helped us make the game a richer and more enjoyable experience. Thanks to you, everything is smoother, deeper and more fun!

This full release is packed with new features and improvements that will take your game to the next level. Thank you for being part of this amazing journey with us.

If you're ready, let's take a look at the brand new features coming with this update!
